{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "workflow_review", "user": "omartinez", "message": "Hi team, our monthly asset inventory check is coming up next week. Please prepare your respective areas for the review.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "cross_departmental", "channel": "collaboration_log_review", "user": "jdoe", "message": "Hey everyone, quick reminder about the interdepartmental meeting this Friday. We will be discussing the Q2 project pipelines. Make sure to review the shared documents beforehand.", "created_at": 1620500500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "workflow_review", "user": "jroberts", "message": "Thanks, Olivia. IT assets have been audited and we've updated the software licenses. We're ready for the inventory check.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "cross_departmental", "channel": "collaboration_log_review", "user": "omartinez", "message": "John, could we also review the Customer Satisfaction Survey results in the meeting? It would be beneficial for product development strategies.", "created_at": 1620501500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "workflow_review", "user": "jdoe", "message": "Understood, Olivia. The production team will make sure all equipment is accounted for and in good condition.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "cross_departmental", "channel": "collaboration_log_review", "user": "jroberts", "message": "Good idea, Olivia. We've been working on updating our CRM system, and the customer feedback would be very useful for the new features we're implementing.", "created_at": 1620502500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "workflow_review", "user": "omartinez", "message": "Great to hear, Jane and John. Let's aim for a smooth asset review. Reach out if you need any assistance.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "cross_departmental", "channel": "collaboration_log_review", "user": "jdoe", "message": "Absolutely, Olivia. I've added the survey review to the meeting agenda. See you all on Friday.", "created_at": 1620503500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "cross_departmental", "channel": "collaboration_log_review", "user": "omartinez", "message": "Hello team, just finished compiling the data from our internal collaboration logs for this year. Between April 1 and December 31, 2025, we conducted 18 cross-departmental workflow planning reviews. This shows a significant increase in our interdepartmental collaboration efforts. Let's keep up the good work!", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
